{"tid":308071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［風骨廢老］於機場襲羅冠聰被控 七旬翁：我唔需要求情","createTime":"2017-07-04T00:24:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-04T07:45:52.000Z","uid":41351,"like":44,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5ae6b63aadf28f1716e67844e46b4d518f263ecb","tid":308071,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T00:24:11.000Z","msg":"涉於機場襲羅冠聰被控 七旬翁：我唔需要求情<br />\n香港眾志立法會議員羅冠聰今年初赴台交流後返港時，在機場遇到示威團體包圍襲擊和淋潑液體。其中一名涉案的七旬退休老翁人今解西九龍法院提訊，被控參與非法集結罪，暫時毋須答辯，押後至本周五與另外4人合併處理。老翁在犯人欄大叫「我唔要律師，我唔需要求情，我反對港獨有錯咩！」，裁判官准他以現金500元保釋，期間不准接觸證人。<br />\n<br />\n71歲被告劉必泉被指於今年1月8日在機場接機大堂與鄺桂嬋、林錦嫦、唐發祥及高傑飛4人在一起作擾亂秩序的行為，導致他人擔心社會安寧被破壞。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56908889&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170703\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56908889%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170703&d=2%2FS89yHObmQ5rGTV%2B1J833Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=b7580e26\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56908889%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170703&h=76d99cd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56908889&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170703</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/04/081958_c37c4f5db8c08ebb58d48ae57e079fff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F04%2F081958_c37c4f5db8c08ebb58d48ae57e079fff.jpg&h=d8feed3b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/04/082002_f6a6ad9c4f5f8c15dac63d0091d526f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F04%2F082002_f6a6ad9c4f5f8c15dac63d0091d526f5.jpg&h=b2a787d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然係廢老五毛，但呢種風骨係本土派睇唔到<br />\n記得黃台仰叫人衝自己坐<br />\n梁頌恆瘋狂追的士，<br />\n陳浩天得個講字<br />\n呢類行動派真係有領袖氣質"},{"pid":"ef61079502ffc408bb1c961bae500a092cc25b61","tid":308071,"uid":7430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T00:27:15.000Z","msg":"駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d335a04c669735f7448d57b23866da0871c4c59","tid":308071,"uid":21392,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T00:30:11.000Z","msg":"樓主數晒咁多派<br />\n硬係有一派冇數臭嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d02e09e810ecf8833efc47e2aba45351c478d34d","tid":308071,"uid":54452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T00:31:41.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de82fb8a6b327ba645db826dede7e04447052dd6","tid":308071,"uid":65818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T00:33:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主數晒咁多派<br />\n硬係有一派冇數臭嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n心水清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a85f46a4c61df61aabed6817946d7bf4a1b82a71","tid":308071,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T00:39:11.000Z","msg":"''風骨'' 係用係文人個度架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa363d3c4824fba4b00d0b8d88d97c8825b66544","tid":308071,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T00:48:08.000Z","msg":"雖然係廢老，不過起碼做得出夠膽認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9841bdf55349e00ff7d1575d14a11b79429ae52c","tid":308071,"uid":20058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T00:48:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主數晒咁多派<br />\n硬係有一派冇數臭嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></